{"tid":1139713,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"計劃五月二十去西藏七天","createTime":"2019-05-05T12:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T16:25:07.000Z","uid":244152,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7aaad2cfaace3e7311128be9dde335d58a177a","tid":1139713,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"大家好，話說見到西藏來回機票4000有找<br />\n勾起左我多年前想去西藏既心願<br />\n<br />\n而目前我也處於待業狀態<br />\n時間相對亦彈性<br />\n<br />\n所以打算去七日，大概必去：<br />\n拉薩，納木錯，林芝，珠峰山腳。<br />\n各位會否到拉薩報當地旅行團到以上地方？<br />\n<br />\n而我自己有哮喘，不過有打開拳<br />\n利申：180cm高，100kg, 30cm長<br />\n提早一星期食定紅景天仲有冇命可以返到香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有依家仲洗唔洗入藏紙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fac3f8417752d0ebb00d5e4bd2b7cd31bc894e","tid":1139713,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"上網check左香港人唔使入藏紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ed1635567f21e833a7ca25dd95d62930ef042b","tid":1139713,"uid":8073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"哮喘未必關事 因為都係要有敏感原先會病發<br />\n不過納木措 珠峰大本營始終海拔都比其他點高<br />\n穩陣既話最好喺大城市林芝拉薩啲藥房買定啲氧氣樽<br />\n一支殺蟲水咁上下大<br />\nbtw如果你包埋頭尾transit得7日既話會好趕<br />\n因為啲景點車程可以講緊6-8個鐘一程<br />\n一日未必去到一點"},{"pid":"d40a5d7a8374fec0adc293b8857ac54081f3b8b5","tid":1139713,"uid":8073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"岩岩先見到你話時間可以彈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好頭兩日stay拉薩適應下先<br />\n尤其你搭飛機<br />\n海拔低啲同埋話晒大城市有咩事啲配套都好啲<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37b562b03bd75d0c556ad1bac4c80168d7f4bb4","tid":1139713,"uid":80332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"去七日會唔會有d趕 見你去林芝又去珠峰 又東又西"},{"pid":"223664b050b217a45ff8209bad2b6294181961aa","tid":1139713,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"預十幾日比較好<br />\n要去公安局搞邊防証先可以入珠峰山腳個邊<br />\n食唔食紅景天冇關係<br />\n要預時間適應"},{"pid":"6850599db36461565479d18ed52d809d3f62ce62","tid":1139713,"uid":103005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"七日應該唔夠<br />\nplan行程要預鬆好過預緊<br />\n有高原反應嘅話<br />\n唔好彩可能頭2日都要訓係拉薩"},{"pid":"122b4cc3cd111b275261bcffee454a79fa8759da","tid":1139713,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:52:55.000Z","msg":"七日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你以為自己去韓國台灣？"},{"pid":"e386d266756e917f9fe32c373c77fee3620aaee1","tid":1139713,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:54:28.000Z","msg":"唔洗返工去足一個月啦"},{"pid":"9467028d8c6b1365f7b964e0302314501ed252f9","tid":1139713,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"準備定身後事。<br />\n<br />\n連高山反應都冇時間適應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你 fit 得過全盛時期嘅許冠傑？<br />\n<br />\n幾乎去尼泊爾冇命返嚟。"},{"pid":"228df3efdd02b1de6175ed3417a6ed34b31719dc","tid":1139713,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40a5d7a8374fec0adc293b8857ac54081f3b8b5","tid":1139713,"uid":8073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"岩岩先見到你話時間可以彈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好頭兩日stay拉薩適應下先<br />\n尤其你搭飛機<br />\n海拔低啲同埋話晒大城市有咩事啲配套都好啲<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"即落林芝，但驚佢過唔到嗰晚。"},{"pid":"ed2ea548a966a4e8ff1179ab9fa6b357e6f6cf74","tid":1139713,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網見啲人一般都去十日以上<br />\n可能未必去珠峰附近<br />\n而去多幾個'錯'<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打