仲洗唔洗入藏紙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"哮喘加打拳就小心<br />\n<br />\n紅景天無用，反而傷身<br />\n睇醫生開高原藥好過<br />\n<br />\n要邊防證，果邊拼車導遊會幫你搞<br />\n<br />\n你揀咩方式都係果個集團包車<br />\n所以揀咩方式都無分別"},{"pid":"347fa4b7cebe01a63e6f00a052ff636aaa724290","tid":1139713,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2ea548a966a4e8ff1179ab9fa6b357e6f6cf74","tid":1139713,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網見啲人一般都去十日以上<br />\n可能未必去珠峰附近<br />\n而去多幾個'錯'<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打試過參加西藏本地團?<br />\n係咪應該十幾日都住拉薩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/719262/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/719262/page/1</a><br />\n追緊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"啲湖海拔都高架<br />\n羊湖4400<br />\n納木錯4900"},{"pid":"5861bc6668621a0e8b1709a4014bfa0d630a9e4c","tid":1139713,"uid":192494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2ea548a966a4e8ff1179ab9fa6b357e6f6cf74","tid":1139713,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網見啲人一般都去十日以上<br />\n可能未必去珠峰附近<br />\n而去多幾個'錯'<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打試過參加西藏本地團?<br />\n係咪應該十幾日都住拉薩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/719262/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/719262/page/1</a><br />\n追緊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"巴打 其實七日真係認真唔夠 你去多幾個錯其實會審美疲勞 不如預多少少時間去埋珠峰好過 再者除左羊卓雍措同納木措之外 其他錯都好難即日來回 <br />\n<br />\n至於join團的話其實就去到邊住到邊 住十幾日拉薩係無需要的"}]}